init_text: When you're 28, science discovers a drug that stops all effects of aging, creating immortality. Your government decides to give the drug to all citizens under 26, but you and the rest of the â€œLost Generations" are deemed too high-risk. When you're 85, the side effects are finally discovered.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You and your friends now have to survive as the earth is being overrun by these zombies.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: On the way to the island, we come across a couple of villages that have survived and are willing to help us.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This is where we will settle.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But then, a group of people arrives on their yacht.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They claim my group are just squatters and that we've taken more than our share.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: My group and the other seniors make an uneasy truce.
